  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C. Take a pan and heat oil over the medium",
    "Put chili, onion, paprika, salt, cumin, and pepper, and cook for 5",
    "minutes.",
    "Add kidney beans, capsicum, water, and tomatoes in it.",
    "After bringing it to boil, put the heat down, and cook for almost 10",
    "minutes.",
    "Put the mixture into four dishes. Fill them with each bean mixture,",
    "and put the egg.",
    "Bake for 15-16 minutes.",
    "Serve with sour cream, coriander, lime, avocado, and tortillas."
